snippet.title: Should Amber Heard Show Up to DC FanDome, or Skip It?
snippet.description:
Should Amber Heard Show Up to DC FanDome, or Skip It? 

Amber Heard's a controversial figure these days, though the media tries to act otherwise. When she posts anything on social media, the backlash is intense, and it's not going to go away.

And if Johnny Depp wins his libel trial, it's going to get even worse.

So should Amber Heard skip the Aquaman 2 panel at DC FanDome, or brave it and see what happens? I guess WB could always turn the comments off, right?

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
